value.value: Adult visual projection neuron with its soma in the brain, posterior to the lateral horn (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It belongs to the SLPpl2 hemilineage (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It has postsynapses in the ipsilateral lobula and the ipsilateral superior clamp (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024).
